ypes\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frazer_Clarke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frazer_Clarke\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the switch\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 574}, {\"ngram\": \"amateur\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 587}, {\"ngram\": \"professional boxing\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 610}, {\"ngram\": \"the footsteps\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 638}, {\"ngram\": \"the likes\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 651}, {\"ngram\": \"recent years\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But a new path could await with WWE having travelled out to Florida for week-long try out at their performance centre.\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 827, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 741, \"end\": 744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\", \"score\": 0.9999932030531435, \"rank\": 6.313597582219738e-06, \"text\": \"WWE\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\"}, {\"begin\": 769, \"end\": 776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"score\": 0.9975985099017399, \"rank\": 0.002330157885017299, \"text\": \"Florida\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a new path\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 723}, {\"ngram\": \"their performance centre\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have been invited to join the WWE, as mad as that sounds,' Orie toldSky Sports.\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 911, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 862, \"end\": 865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\", \"score\": 0.9999932030531435, \"rank\": 6.313597582219738e-06, \"text\": \"WWE\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Orie toldSky Sports\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 910}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was a fantastic experience, I learned so much over the few days I was there.\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 993, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fantastic experience\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 943}, {\"ngram\": \"the few days\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 980}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's definitely I have something on the table as an option.'\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1054, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1026}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1039}, {\"ngram\": \"an option\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked about the offer, Orie continued: 'It is real.\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1107, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the offer\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1077}, {\"ngram\": \"Orie\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1083}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I got the message over the Olympics, at the time I was just focused on the Games.\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1189, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the message\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1125}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1143}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1156}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1188}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After than when I was on holiday I was slowly replying to all these messages, initially I thought it was a scam.\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1302, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"holiday\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1222}, {\"ngram\": \"all these messages\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1266}, {\"ngram\": \"a scam\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They said, \\\"we see your potential and we would like to work with you\\\".'\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1374, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your potential\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1336}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Orie is also expected to receive offers to stay in